sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor WP as Wajib Pajak
    participant UI as Pengaturan dan SPPT UI
    participant VM as Settings dan SPPT ViewModel
    participant ReminderRepo as PaymentReminderRepository
    participant Worker as WorkManager
    participant System as Android Notification

    WP->>UI: Aktifkan pengingat jatuh tempo
    UI->>VM: setReminderEnabled(true)
    alt Android 13+ belum ada izin notifikasi
        UI-->>WP: Minta izin POST_NOTIFICATIONS
        WP-->>UI: Beri izin
    end
    VM->>ReminderRepo: Simpan preferensi aktif
    ReminderRepo-->>VM: OK

    WP->>UI: Buka Histori SPPT atau Tunggakan
    UI->>VM: load tagihan
    VM->>ReminderRepo: scheduleUnpaidBills(tagihan belum lunas)
    ReminderRepo->>Worker: Jadwalkan 30 7 dan 1 hari sebelum jatuh tempo
    Worker-->>ReminderRepo: Work request tersimpan
    ReminderRepo-->>VM: Jadwal reminder
    VM-->>UI: Tampilkan daftar notifikasi
    UI-->>WP: Lihat jadwal pengingat

    Worker->>System: Kirim trigger saat jadwal tercapai
    System-->>WP: Notifikasi pengingat PBB tanpa NIK atau alamat lengkap
